Class UserToReviewerMapping

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.neu.ccis.sms.entity.users.UserToReviewerMapping
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    @Entity
public class UserToReviewerMapping
extends Object
implements Serializable, Comparable<UserToReviewerMapping>
    Hibernate Entity bean class for UserToReviewerMapping; Contain user to reviewer mappings i.e. user's submissions will be reviewed by which evaluators, for which submission,which submittable member etc.
